PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?governmentType ?governmentTypeLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q796 wdt:P122 ?governmentType .
  ?governmentType rdfs:label ?governmentTypeLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?governmentTypeLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?senator ?senatorLabel WHERE {
  ?senator p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q161549 ; pq:P937 wd:Q1370 .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?statement pq:P580 ?start
  }
  .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?statement pq:P582 ?end
  }
  .
  FILTER ( ( YEAR( ?start ) <= 2013 && ( YEAR( ?end ) >= 2013 || ?end = "infinity" @en ) ) || ( YEAR( ?start ) <= 2013 && ! BOUND( ?end ) ) ) .
  ?senator rdfs:label ?senatorLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?senatorLabel ) = "en" )
}
ORDER BY ?senatorLabel

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?coach WHERE {
  wd:Q330120 wdt:P286 ?coach .

}
